: 
<bibRefCitation id="56D8AC558543A4DFDE1D8EC000353363" author="Mortensen, T" journalOrPublisher="CA Reitzel, Copenhagen" pageId="7" pageNumber="78" title="A Monograph of the Echinoidea. III, 1. Aulodonta, with Additions to Vol. II (Lepidocentroida and Stirodonta)." year="1940">Mortensen 1940</bibRefCitation>
