<bibRefCitation id="E197D2F4A427E3619A7D82AD6FD0D221" pageId="2" pageNumber="73">Clark and Rowe 1971</bibRefCitation>
: 153, fig. 64a [description and distribution]; 
<bibRefCitation id="22636DCDD5F85D1E3440F180B1C2C5E7" author="Samyn, Y" journalOrPublisher="Journal of East African Natural History" pageId="7" pageNumber="78" pagination="1 - 34" title="Annotated checklist of the echinoderms from the Kiunga Marine National Reserve, Kenya - Part I: Echinoidea and Holothuroidea." volume="89" year="2000">Samyn and Vanden Berghe 2000</bibRefCitation>
